<td width="600" colspan="4">
<b>Description</b><br>
This item is dropped by the Goblin Bodyguard, who can be found in the Temple of Droga.  He drops the Circlet of Shadows as the common loot, the Whip of Stragulation as the uncommon loot, and the Gauntlets of Potence as his rare drop.</td>
